{"tid":1500951,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[推上熱門]運動失焦！入黎傾香港人Agenda！","createTime":"2019-08-24T08:02:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T10:38:04.000Z","uid":100976,"like":20,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"52dff4314e56500b377a32530cfd16c47968522d","tid":1500951,"uid":100976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:02:56.000Z","msg":"而家政府開始吹和風，大家開始搞和理非等政府出招，你以為開始有希望？<br />\n錯啦！咁只係證明<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地開始輸！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以等政府比<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">袋住先</span></strong></span>方案！<br />\n我地應該要主動比方案政府，政府只可以決定<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">接受或者唔接受</span></span></strong>！<br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得雨傘點輸？就係輸在同政府慢慢談判而<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">運動失焦！</span></strong></span><br />\n運動永遠都係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>被拖死</strong></span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要贏，就要我地自己Set Agenda!</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要贏，就要我地自己Set Agenda!</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要贏，就要我地自己Set Agenda!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n點解冇人再討論運動方向？因為政府真係開始回應，真係開始推溝通平台<br />\n但係大家都知溝通平台代表唔到所有人<br />\n咁我地可以點做？<br />\n<br />\n首先，我地要<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>承認場運動係冇可能無止境繼續</strong></span></span><br />\n就算我地搞足一年、兩年、三年，始終都會完<br />\n我地要諗定完左可以點，社會大多數人都仍然希望社會恢復穩定，亦係和理非心底裏想見到個畫面，只係政府未比滿意方案，大家冇辦法妥協讓步 (我知有可能係一碌鳩打一船人，但起碼西瓜派肯定咁諗)<br />\n溝通平台代表唔到所有人，我地就<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔應該認真對待呢個Agenda!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>但係我地要食住個勢改變個風向，所以必須回應政府，但係</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">回應應該要有其他目標！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n妥協讓步唔緊要！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">只要政府認錯同埋比權力我地</span></strong></span>！<br />\n整個運動目標應該係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">奪權! 奪權! 奪權!</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲記唔記得被DQ果幾個議員？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而家政府要建立溝通平台，<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>得！就推果幾個被DQ議員入溝通平台！</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>咁做目的係要政府認錯！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以比政府亂求其搵堆人代表全港市民！<br />\n政府要比誠意，就必須承認之前做錯！<br />\n<br />\n如果全香港都認同<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>被DQ議員有公信力，應該由佢地作為代表進入溝通平台</strong></span></span>，咁政府就必須回應呢個我地比出黎D人選，<br />\n而且只可以回答<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">是或者否</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求唔可以放棄！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n但要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>香港人真正贏返次，就要有清晰Agenda！<br />\n</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n政府<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唔比被DQ議員入溝通平台，就係假溝通！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果政府比佢地入溝通平台，即係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">承認中共DQ議員係錯！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果推<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">梁游入溝通平台，就代表HONG KONG IS NOT CHINA係啱！！！<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span>認同請正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔認同就提出其他<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>政府只可以回答是或否嘅方案</strong></span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n利申：冷氣軍師，知大家攰，但唔想輸呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0619fd854421db181ae4b8ad90274d622bdf308","tid":1500951,"uid":100976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:21:12.000Z","msg":"自推！"},{"pid":"520729ca5b435c3984296db0d237becdcf86b128","tid":1500951,"uid":100976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:29:22.000Z","msg":"自推！"},{"pid":"76647d0bd033b83b70b02d8049fa34999678a9ad","tid":1500951,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:32:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4b5b4efa24090ea1164bd2e8f9d78a764b2ab2fd","tid":1500951,"uid":114802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T08:35:34.000Z","msg":"梁游？不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>五大訴求，缺一不可</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">獨立調查 撒回惡法 平反暴動 撒銷檢控</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">雙真普選</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>堅拒階段性勝利！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全民文宣鍵戰</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各區連儂牆、airdrop、派街招、擺街站、facebook &amp; instagram瘋狂轉貼文宣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每人一個twitter account，like &amp; retweet 有關反送中的消息<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全面推廣中共納粹主義，增加國際迴響 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>#ChiNazism</strong></spa